## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the lack of direct empirical studies specifically linking reflective practice to reduced compassion fatigue and burnout in nurses. Most available literature discusses reflective practice as part of broader self-care strategies. Additionally, the effectiveness of reflective practice may vary based on individual differences and the specific work environment.

